               <msContents class="#CM">
                  <summary><p>The palm-leaf bundle, a probably composite manuscript, entitled <title xml:lang="ta">Viratam Aintu</title> on its additional title page, contains:
  <list>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Citamparacakkaram</title> (Indien 10a).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Pōkar Pūcāviti</title> (Indien 10b).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Koṅkaṇar Pūcāviti</title> (Indien 10c).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Koṅkaṇar Pāṭal</title> (Indien 10d).</item>
  <item>The <title xml:lang="ta">Varākimālai Mūlamantiram</title> (Indien 10e).</item>
  </list></p></summary>
                  
                  
